These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-1::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: punk, ambient, dubstep, house
1. the fan of ambient is between the fan of dubstep and the fan of house##2
2. the fan of ambient is on the left of the fan of dubstep##1
3. the fan of punk is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |  2   |  3   |   4   |
| Music-Genre   | punk | house | ambient | dubstep |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, juice, milk, 7up
1. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
2. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
3. the person drinking 7up is between the person drinking juice and the person drinking lemonade##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |  3   |    4     |
| Beverage   | juice | 7up | lemonade | milk |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-3::.
4 different pets are kept: goldfish, hedgehog, lizard, frog
1. the owner of the frog is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1
2. the owner of the lizard is between the owner of the hedgehog and the owner of the frog##2
3. the owner of the goldfish is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |  1   |   2    |  3   |   4    |
| Pet   | goldfish | frog | lizard | hedgehog |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-4::.
There 4 different types of food: peas, avocado, lettuce, pomegranate
1. the person eating lettuce is between the person eating avocado and the person eating peas##2
